room_title: Escape room "Time Traveler" by Masterminds Escape Room and Game Library in Mansfield
room_description: Since the 80's, time travel has been a mass-produced technology available only to the most wealthy. Numerous prototypes were sold on the market. In the midst of your travel, the time machine malfunctions, leaving you stuck in the time of its creation. Do you have what it takes to be the MASTERMIND, and fix the machine, returning to present time before the machine self-destructs?
